Instruction of AdaWong

The improvements in V2 are as follows:

1. I manually eliminated the watermark of the training imgs, now the generated imgs will no longer have a watermark

2. The images generated by V2 are more colorful and no longer blurred like V1

3. V2 is more compatible with realistic checkpoints than V1

***1. if the standing pose is always the same, please increase the weight of standing;

***2. Increase the weight of beautiful face can make the face more realistic, but it may deviate from Ada's appearance in the game

AdaWongV2说明

相比V1，V2的改进如下：

1.我手动消除了训练集的水印，现在生成的图片不会再有水印了

2.V2生成的图片色彩更加丰富，不会再像V1一样发白

3.与真人模型的契合度更高，生成的角色更加逼真，尤其是脸部

V2使用说明：

关键词：Ada_re4, (((beautiful face))), 1girl,black hair, short hair, red sweater, belt, black thigh boots

Lora权重：0.6~0.8（不要设置的太高）

***注意事项：1.如果站立姿势总是不变，请提高standing的权重；

2.提高beautiful face的权重可以使脸部更加接近真人，但可能会偏离Ada在游戏中的样貌

————————————————————————————————————————

兄弟们，新鲜出炉的王阿姨王姐姐来啦~例图在上面，不要用太高的分辨率生成图像，强烈建议使用高分修复，我自己设定的高分修复生成参数如下：

Ada Wong in Resident Evil 4, the trigger word is Ada_re4. Don't generate images at too high resolution, and I strongly recommend using Hires. fix to generate the images, The following picture is for reference：

items.name: Pixel style lora 像素化lora
items.description:
这是一个由32*32像素的素材训练而来的lora。它实际并不能让你的图片产生严格的32*32级别像素，因为目前AI做不到。总的来说，它是一个像素风格的lora，它的作用是使你的图片像素化。

具体作用：

1.填写单个物品或者简图案时，可以使你的画面强烈地像素化。你可以根据权重调整像素化的程度（见参考图）。你可以结合角色lora来玩，挺有趣的，也许可以做一些风格化的表情图案？

2.稍微复杂一些的图片，根据权重（0.6到1.5）会呈现出“被像素化”到“像素玩偶”的一个状态（见参考图）。

3.在inpainting里使用的话，会产生马赛克的效果。

注意：如果你使用Hires. Fix的话，Denoising需要调低。

This is a lora trained on materials with a resolution of 3232 pixels. It cannot strictly produce images with a resolution of 3232 pixels, as AI cannot currently achieve that. In general, it is a pixel style lora that pixelates your images.

Its functions are as follows:

1.When filling in a single item or simple pattern, it can strongly pixelate your image. You can adjust the degree of pixelation according to the weight (see reference image). You can also combine it with character lorae for fun and perhaps create some stylized emoticons.

2.For slightly more complex images, depending on the weight（0.6to1.5）, it will present a state of being "pixelated" to "pixel doll" (see reference image).

3.When used in inpainting, it produces a mosaic effect.

Note: If you use Hires. Fix, you need to reduce the denoising.

items.name: MeteoriteDiffusion
items.description:
Hello again gentle men. Today I have a different model for ya'll today. This time this model looks a little bit similar to other models. However its the way this model generates it characters is interesting. Imagine a semi realistic model, however the characters feel like they've been ripped right outta a 2010's anime. That's how this model is.

After playing around with some mixes N stuff I stumbled upon a mix where its pretty complicated and will require a lot of explaining. This model can create very nice looking photos that have a very Nanoless (artisit) feel to them. (I did not use there art work in any way. This is only a mix from various anime models.)

Below is the recommended settings for this model:

  • CFG Scale 6

  • Steps for Test: 20.

  • Steps for Illustration: 50.

  • Upscaler (Latent, works really well with the outlines this model creates)

  • Sampler (PLMS and UniPC work good. But the best one for all around is DPM Adaptive)

This model creates that good stuff. And when I mean it, I mean it big time. This model might be even more efficient than my BMM model I made. But this model is brand spanking new. Not Like BMM which I created a while back but now share it with yall. Anyways, this model can also create good NSFW due to Ambrosia and Anything as well as some Grapefruit sprinkled in. This is all around general needs model. In fact, it can even create stunning land scapes! Below is yadadada you know the drill, photos below are used with all of the steps above. (Photos made with PLMS cause its cool.)

items.name: Pokémon (Style)
items.description:
LoRA trained on the animefull-final model using the official artwork of the mainline Pokémon games. I'd personally recommend using this the most with AnythingV3.

For full body shots I'd suggesting using a resolution of 448x896, as this was the largest bucket in the dataset. Most resolutions still work quite well though and which you want to use can depend a lot on the pose/character you want to depict.

All artwork has been tagged with their respective generation (eg. generation 1, generation 2, etc.). Allowing you to get different styles, occasionally there's a bit of bleeding (mostly at gens 3 and 4) but its fairly consistent otherwise.

As for upscaling, I recommend using something like the anime ESRGAN models, rather than the default latent upscaling. As the Pokémon artstyle doesn't have a lot of details any new stuff added usually looks bad.

My Twitter: https://twitter.com/KbrLoras

- Tensor.art (free online generation)

Please consider supporting me at: https://ko-fi.com/kbrloras

It takes time and effort to collect training materials, training, testing LORAS, I would appreciate your support!

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Introduction
1. This version or KDL does not necessarily mean it is better or worse than v10 or v15, it is a different version that feature another set variety of faces.

Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • VAE: vae-ft-mse-840000-ema-pruned (For realistic models)

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • Steps: 20 to 35

  • Clipskip: 1 or 2

  • Upscaler : Latent (bicubic antialiased)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: anywhere between 0.2 to 0.7 are recommended

  • Denoise strength for img2img: 0.4 to 0.7

  • It is also recommended to mix this LORA with my other DollLikeness LORAs for interesting effects

items.name: YumemiHoshino(星野梦美)-Planetarian(星之梦)
items.description:
V2.0

2.0的泛化有稍微降低，推荐权重1，此次更新主要是fullbody的特化，对下半身服装做了一定优化，所以对Tag：fullbody极为敏感，谨慎使用。使用2.0建议加入视角类，姿势类Tag，否则您可能会得到单一姿势的生成图，咱一直在追求服饰配饰的还原度，但进度缓慢，只能慢慢来。顺便，2.0直出图可能质量普遍有所降低，所以想要高质量出图更依赖于高清修复，Tag尽量详细，这都是出高质量图的必要条件。

2.0 generalization has slightly reduced, recommended weight 1, this update is mainly fullbody specialization, the lower body clothing to do some optimization, so extremely sensitive to Tag: fullbody, use with caution. Using 2.0 is recommended to add perspective class, pose class Tag, otherwise you may get a single pose generation chart, we have been in pursuit of the degree of restoration of clothing and accessories, but the progress is slow, only slowly!By the way, the quality of 2.0 straight images may generally decrease, so high-quality images rely more on high-definition repair, and tags should be as detailed as possible. These are all necessary conditions for producing high-quality images.

2.0の汎化はやや低下しており、重み1を推奨しているが、今回のアップデートは主にフルボディに特化しており、下半身の服装に一定の最適化をしているため、Tag：フルボディに極めて敏感で、慎重に使用している。2.0を使って画角類、姿勢類Tagを加えることを提案します。そうしないと、単一の姿勢の生成図が得られる可能性があります。私たちはずっと服飾アクセサリーの還元度を求めていますが、進度は遅く、ゆっくりしかできません。ちなみに、2.0直出図は一般的に品質が低下している可能性があるので、高品質出図をよりハイビジョン修復に依存したい場合は、Tagをできるだけ詳細にすることが高品質図を出すための必要条件です。

V1.0

推荐权重0.6左右，请根据不同Checkpoint模型进行不同的权重调整，以达到最佳效果
测试Anything4.5，DOSMIX，PVCStyleModel，CounterfeitV25等Checkpoints模型的兼容性都不错
缺点：背景容易异常，发光缎带容易异常，以后可能会进行优化

请勿使用本模型生成的图片发往Pixiv！

请勿使用本模型生成R18发往公众平台！

若发现违规，本人将会删除此模型。

The recommended weight is around 0.6. Please adjust the weight according to different Checkpoint models to achieve the best results

Testing the compatibility of Checkpoints models such as Anything4.5, DOSMIX, PVCStyleModel, and CounterfeitV25 is good

Disadvantages: The background is prone to abnormalities, and the luminous ribbon is prone to abnormalities, which may be optimized in the future

Do not use the images generated by this model to send to Pixiv!

Do not use this model to generate R18 and send it to the public platform!

If any violations are found, I will delete this model.

Anything 4.5、DOSMIX、PVC StyleModel、CounterfeitV 25などのCheckpointsモデルの互換性をテストするのに良い

Default outfit: blue dress

Fire Flower: red dress

Halloween: witch dress, witch hat

Biker: bikesuit

Swimwear: swimwear, flower

Chef: chef, apron

Tennis: tenniswear, white pantyhose

Volendam: volendamse dress, white hat

items.name: Rick Vtuber Model
items.description:
This is my first time training a model, but i hope you enjoy:

if you're using the v1 dont forget to use the tags: full_body, virtual_youtuber, standing.

It works with anything 3 to 4.5 and models that use a similar dataset.

if you're using the v2 version i recommend you to use the MeinaMix and you don't need any tags, but if you model is being cut use "full_body", and depending on the tags you use for the characteristics you may need to add "straight-on".

if you need help feel free to send a msg on the discord:
https://discord.gg/mZpWrdcZVz

modelVersions.name: v2.0
modelVersions.description:
Just a update for the model, this version is making more coherent models.

This time i trained the hypernet using the MeinaMix model, so i recommend you to use the same:

https://civitai.com/models/7240/meinamix

Now you are not obliged to add the tags virtual_youtuber, standing, fullbody. But if you model is being cut use "full_body", and depending on the tags you use for the characteristics you may need to add "straight-on".

BR --

Esse é um update da versão anterior, ela consegue criar modelos mais coerentes e erra um pouco menos nos detalhes.

Eu treinei a hypernet usando o MeinaMix, então eu recomendo vocês usarem o mesmo modelo, não tenho certeza se funciona em outros.

https://civitai.com/models/7240/meinamix

Não é mais obrigatório usar as tags: virtual_youtuber, standing, fullbody. Mas se você ver que seu modelo está sendo cortado, pode querer usar full_body, e dependendo das tags que você coloca para as características do modelo, pode querer usar "straight-on" para ajudar ele a ficar na posição.
